Richard Sherman shared a photo of him and his girlfriend Ashley Moss with their son Rayden on Instagram .
The Seahawks lost the Super Bowl to the New England Patriots on February 5, just four days after Sherman and Moss welcomed a son, Rayden .
In the most recent photo, Sherman posted to Instagram that he and Moss were cradling Rayden, with the football star writing: 'Best part of Life'
It was just announced the Seahawks would play the Denver Broncos in their first preseason game .